<ul class="blockList">
<li class="blockList">
<h4>getRemoteRegistry</h4>
<pre>java.rmi.registry.Registry&nbsp;getRemoteRegistry(java.lang.String&nbsp;host)</pre>
<div class="block">Returns the RMI Registry on a remote machine on port
